OL,7,FQuestions will surely be raised about
OL,8,Fwhy he continued to receive his large
OL,9,Fsalary for five months after his
OL,10,Farrest on charges of making indecent
OL,11,Fphotographs of children.
OL,13,FThis last salary marked a #40,000 pay
OL,14,Frise from 2022/23, when he was paid
OL,15,Fbetween #435,000 and 439,999.
OL,17,FThe BBC has said that if Edwards had
OL,18,Fbeen charged while he was still an
OL,19,Femployee it would have sacked him, but
OL,20,Fat the point of charge he no longer
OL,21,Fworked for the corporation.
