OL,7,FAfter his guilty plea, a BBC
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "In November 2023,
OL,9,Fwhilst Mr Edwards was suspended, the
OL,10,FBBC as his employer at the time was
OL,11,Fmade aware in confidence that he had
OL,12,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of serious
OL,13,Foffences and released on bail whilst
OL,14,Fthe police continued their
OL,15,Finvestigation.
OL,17,F"At the time, no charges had been
OL,18,Fbrought against Mr Edwards and the BBC
OL,19,Fhad also been made aware of
OL,20,Fsignificant risk to his health."
