OL,7,FThe corporation added: "The BBC is
OL,8,Fshocked to hear the details which have
OL,9,Femerged in court today. There can be
OL,10,Fno place for such abhorrent behaviour
OL,11,Fand our thoughts are with all those
OL,12,Faffected.
OL,14,F"Today we have learnt of the
OL,15,Fconclusion of the police process in
OL,16,Fthe details as presented to the court.
