OL,7,FThe government is likely to question
OL,8,FDavie about whether Edwards' salary
OL,9,Fwas the best use of the money
OL,10,Fgenerated by the licence fee, which
OL,11,Fthe public currently pays #169.50 a
OL,12,Fyear for.
OL,14,FThe fact Edwards has now admitted
OL,15,Fthree charges of making indecent
OL,16,Fphotographs ` after he was sent 41
OL,17,Fillegal images by convicted paedophile
OL,18,FAlex Williams ` will also likely raise
OL,19,Fserious questions of trust in figures
OL,20,Fat the BBC.
