OL,7,FAt the time the annual report was
OL,8,Fpublished, Davie defended Edwards'
OL,9,F#40,000 pay rise, saying: "We are
OL,10,Falways trying to be very judicious
OL,11,Fwith the spending of public money and
OL,12,Fno-one wants to waste a pound.
OL,14,F"But what you're trying to do, and
OL,15,Ffrom the onset of that affair, was
OL,16,Ftrying to act proportionally, fairly
OL,17,Fand navigate this appropriately.
OL,19,F"I think that's what we did... but I
OL,20,Fthink we wouldn't have wasted money if
OL,21,Fwe weren't doing the right thing."
